CBRE is pleased to offer 500 Churchill Road, Kilburn SA for lease and available immediately. 

The property is located in the established industrial area of Kilburn being some 8km northwest of the Adelaide CBD. The property is situated on Churchill Road and in close proximity to Grand Junction Road.

The property features:
• Large fenced and secure laydown area with hardstand available 
• B-Double Access
• Ability to be leased as whole or half
• Affordable rental terms available 
• Multiple roller door access 
• High clearance warehouse area
• Recently refurbished office area 
• Efficient access to major freight corridors
• Areas from 1,000 sqm 
• Flexible lease terms
• Attractive incentives offered
• Additional high clearance warehousing of 1,200sqm* available nearby on the industrial estate.
